369
00:17:33,464 --> 00:17:35,034
{\pos(192,220)}Oh, now what?

370
00:17:35,036 --> 00:17:36,500
{\pos(192,220)}You want me
to throw him out?

371
00:17:36,517 --> 00:17:37,712
{\pos(192,220)}No, that's okay.

372
00:17:37,767 --> 00:17:39,841
{\pos(192,220)}Are you sure? He's small.

373
00:17:40,450 --> 00:17:42,916
I bet I can get a nice,
tight spiral on him.

